<br>
<b>Rant Forum is a place where community members can let loose</b><br>
<br>
<u>Believe the only requirement is:</u><br>
 - Use your main Character's Name<br>
<br>
<u>I try to use Common sense when posting Rants:</u><br>
 - Your not selling a car - your just expressing your feelings.<br>
 - Speak the truth, its your reputation on the line<br>
 - Here say (sp) = Not your rant, again its your reputation<br>
 - Swearing degrades the post overall, though sometimes its more of an expression then an attack.  Overall its not necessary, but when your "pissed" off it does come out.<br>
 - I don't mind calling people an idiot or moronic - though constant use degrades the post.<br>
 - If its your rant - don't post with your guild tags unless your guild knows you are going to rant about this or that.<br>
 - Mistakes in communication doesn't constitute a rant unless there is a history of mis-communication with this or that person or this or that guild.<br>
 - Try to resolve issues w/in the game first - /guildleaders are very good at handling there own people. <br>
 - No Rules for VI/SOE = Open Target<br>
 - Any Sexual comments are to be serverely repremanded by the community at large, if it continues banning should be requested.<br>
 - Any REAL LIFE threats should be deleted and that person should be banned.<br>
 - Poppycock is not a swear!<br>
<br>
These are guidelines - nothing to be adheared to.. not something you may follow.. but I <b>try</b> to stay w/in my own guidelines<br>
<br>
The Forum is for Rants - if you can't handle, stomach or are offended by words.. actions or complaints.. then you need to stop reading it.<br>
<br>
<i>Earth... lets not ruin it</i><br>
